' DEMO 2.5 - Roller axis accuracy
' Roller 1.5in dia, circumference = 4.712in
' Commanded 1 full rev = 8192 counts = 4.712in linear on roller surface
' Mark a line on the roller, run move, measure with caliper
' Compare _DPA (actual encoder position) to commanded

#main
MO A
SH A
KPA=10
KDA=64
KIA=0
LDA=3
ACA=2000000
DCA=2000000
SPC=40000
DPA=0

PRA=8192
BG A
AM A

MG "Commanded=8192  Actual=",_DPA

MO A
EN
